docs.text:
d-phpmyadmin


phpMyAdmin is a web interface for interacting with 
MySQL databases. This is run as part of the charlesreid1.com
docker pod.


To run a stock image:


./run_stock_phpmyadmin.sh




To run as part of a docker pod,
see 
pod-charlesreid1
.
